										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p class="has-drop-cap">Your Furniture is no longer just an item to place in your home but rather an opportunity to express yourself. Thus, it becomes important that you have the right kind of decor in your personal and professional environment.In our daily lives, the decor creates and enhances our living environment. Thus, it becomes very important to have the best furniture for our comfort needs where we can relax and enjoy our personal time.</p>



<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Top 10 Furniture Brands in 2024</h2>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">1. &nbsp;<a href="https://www.stickley.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Stickley</a></h3>



<p>They provide you with classical furniture choices that not only create a luxurious environment around you but also appreciate in value, as the design is timeless.</p>



<p>The furniture they produce lasts a long time, thus creating excellent value for money. Even though their furniture might cost a little more than the other options on the list, the extra cost is worth the quality they provide.</p>



<p>You will be provided with the option to choose from oak and cherry along with 7 different options in stains. The customizable options are not vast but they make up for it with long-lasting furniture.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1006" src="https://www.urbancraftoasis.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/stickley-1.webp" alt="Stickley Home page" class="wp-image-3343"/></figure>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">2. &nbsp;<a href="https://smithbrothersfurniture.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Smith Brothers Furniture</a></h3>



<p>If you are looking for a highly customizable furniture brand, then Smith Brothers will perfectly fit your requirements.</p>


<div class="wp-block-image">
<figure class="alignleft size-full"><img decoding="async" width="225" height="225" src="https://www.urbancraftoasis.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Untitled.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-3416"/></figure></div>


<p>They mainly focus on living room furniture, with attention to detail which rivals any other brand and surpasses them. The furniture is sturdy and long-lasting. Thus, if you are someone who wants a purchase a piece of furniture that lasts through generations then Smith Brothers Furniture will be the perfect fit.</p>



<p>Their sofas don&#8217;t have the generic sinuous springs that are used in most sofas. They use a coil spring system that individually supports each section of the sofa so that people sitting on it won&#8217;t cave into each other.</p>



<p>Customization and reliability are what differentiates them from other brands. In customization, you will have the option to choose the frame and the fabric.</p>



<p>In their sofa sections, they have the 3000, 5000, 8000, and 9000 series where you can choose the frame and have customized armrest style, leg, and back. You can customize it according to your preferences.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1920" height="1063" src="https://www.urbancraftoasis.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/smithbrothersfurniture-1.webp" alt="Smith Brothers Furniture Home Page" class="wp-image-3344"/></figure>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">3. &nbsp;<a href="https://www.sherrillfurniture.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sherrill Furniture</a></h3>



<p>They provide you with handmade custom furniture. This furniture is comparatively less expensive than other options on this list.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-pullquote"><blockquote><p>Even though they are reasonably priced they make no compromise with the quality.</p></blockquote></figure>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1920" height="896" src="https://www.urbancraftoasis.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Craftmaster_Furniture-1.webp" alt="Sherrill Furniture Home Page" class="wp-image-3345"/></figure>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">4. &nbsp;<a href="https://vaughanbassett.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vaughan Bassett</a></h3>



<p>If you are looking for some trendy designs then Vaughan Bassett is the brand for you. You will get the best and most trendy designs and also have the option to make custom changes according to your preferences.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1123" src="https://www.urbancraftoasis.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Vaughan_Bassett-1.webp" alt="Vaughan Bassett Home Page" class="wp-image-3346"/></figure>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">5. &nbsp;<a href="https://www.englandfurniture.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">England Furniture</a></h3>



<p>If you are looking for affordable and long-lasting furniture then this is the brand for you.</p>



<blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow">
<p>They offer a 10-year cushion core warranty; thus, they stand by their product for 10 years. If you find the frame to be too weak, they also avail a frame coil upgrade.</p>
</blockquote>



<p>They will offer everything you need for your living room with hundreds of fabrics to choose from and multiple leather options.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1284" src="https://www.urbancraftoasis.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/England_Furniture-1.webp" alt="England Furniture Home Page" class="wp-image-3347"/></figure>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">6. &nbsp;<a href="https://www.cmfurniture.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Craft Master</a></h3>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1920" height="896" src="https://www.urbancraftoasis.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Craftmaster_Furniture-2.webp" alt="Craft Master Home Page" class="wp-image-3348"/></figure>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">7. &nbsp;<a href="https://www.la-z-boy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">La-Z-Boy</a></h3>



<p>Lay-Z-Boy is a large manufacturer that has many sub-brands with their own specializations.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="720" height="118" src="https://www.urbancraftoasis.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lay_z_boy1-1-1.webp" alt="" class="wp-image-3349"/></figure>



<ol class="wp-block-list">
<li>Lay-Z-Boy Residentitals</li>



<li>Hammery</li>



<li>England Furniture</li>



<li>Kineaid Furniture</li>



<li>American Drew</li>
</ol>



<p>Being a big manufacturer, it not only deals with recliners and sofas but many different types of furniture. Thus, giving you a wide array of options to choose from, for your home decor.</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1920" height="929" src="https://www.urbancraftoasis.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/lay_z_boy-1.webp" alt="La-Z-Boy Home Page" class="wp-image-3350"/></figure>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">8. <a href="https://www.indiana-furniture.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Indiana Furniture and Mattresses</a></h3>



<p>Based in the Indiana area, they started manufacturing in 1962 and grew into one of the best furniture brands. Best Home Furnishings is known for its lift chairs, recliners, and customizable sofas.</p>



<p></p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1920" height="976" src="https://www.urbancraftoasis.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Indiana_Furniture_crop-1.webp" alt="Indiana Furniture and Mattresses Home Page" class="wp-image-3351"/></figure>


 
